{"content":"<h3 id=\"Database-evolutions-support-in-a-separate-module\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px 9px; padding: 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-family: HelveticaNeue-CondensedBold, 'Open Sans Condensed', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\">Database evolutions support in a separate module</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3em; max-width: 840px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Support for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.4.x/Evolutions\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(84, 139, 12);\">database evolutions</a>&nbsp;used to be included with both Play JDBC and JPA support. That¡¯s no longer the case. Therefore, if you are using evolutions, you now need to add an explicit dependency to&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">evolutions</code>&nbsp;in your project¡¯s build:</p><pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; padding: 2px 40px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); line-height: 15px;\"><code class=\"language-scala\" style=\"margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 4px; background-image: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: inherit;\"><span class=\"pln\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">libraryDependencies </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 0);\">+=</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> evolutions</span></code></pre><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3em; max-width: 840px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">While, if you are not using evolutions, you can now safely remove<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">evolutionplugin=disabled</code>&nbsp;from your&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">application.conf</code>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3em; max-width: 840px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">The configuration keys have changed, so instead of&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">evolutionplugin=disabled</code>you now need to use&nbsp;<code style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inconsolata, monospace; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;\">play.evolutions.enabled=false</code>&nbsp;(See&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.4.x/Evolutions#Evolutions-configuration\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(84, 139, 12);\">Evolutions configuration</a>)</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.3em; max-width: 840px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">If you are using Play Slick module (with or without evolutions), things have changed quite a bit, so make sure to read the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.4.x/PlaySlickMigrationGuide\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(84, 139, 12);\">Play Slick migration guide</a>.</p>","title":"Database evolutions support in a separate module","tag":"Play 2.4","datePublish":"2015-09-11T01:21:47.014Z"}